            </div>
            <div class="principle-card">
                <div class="principle-icon">ü§ù</div>
                <h3>Respect</h3>
                <p>Treat everyone with dignity, even when you disagree</p>
            </div>
            <div class="principle-card">
                <div class="principle-icon">‚ú®</div>
                <h3>Authenticity</h3>
                <p>Be genuine, honest, and true to yourself</p>
            </div>
            <div class="principle-card">
                <div class="principle-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
                <h3>Safety</h3>
                <p>Help maintain a harassment-free environment for all</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>What We Encourage</h2>
        <ul class="encouraged-list">
            <li>üìä <strong>Share Your Progress:</strong> Post about your achievements, milestones, and growth journey</li>
            <li>üí° <strong>Helpful Content:</strong> Share tips, resources, and insights that help others improve</li>
            <li>üéØ <strong>Goal Setting:</strong> Discuss your goals, challenges, and strategies for success</li>
            <li>ü§ó <strong>Supportive Feedback:</strong> Offer constructive criticism and genuine encouragement</li>
            <li>üåü <strong>Celebrate Others:</strong> Recognize and applaud the achievements of fellow users</li>
            <li>üìö <strong>Knowledge Sharing:</strong> Teach skills, share what you've learned</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What's Not Allowed</h2>
        
        <h3>üö´ Harassment & Hate Speech</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Bullying, threats, or intimidation of any kind</li>
            <li>Hate speech based on race, ethnicity, religion, gender, sexual orientation, disability, or any other protected characteristic</li>
            <li>Unwanted sexual advances or inappropriate comments</li>
            <li>Doxxing or sharing private information without consent</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>üö´ Harmful Content</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Content promoting self-harm, suicide, or eating disorders</li>
            <li>Graphic violence or gore</li>
            <li>Content glorifying dangerous activities</li>
            <li>Sexually explicit or pornographic material</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>üö´ Misinformation & Spam</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Deliberately spreading false information</li>
            <li>Spam, repetitive content, or bot-like behavior</li>
            <li>Fake engagement (buying followers, likes, etc.)</li>
            <li>Phishing or scam attempts</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>üö´ Illegal Activities</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Promoting illegal drugs or substances</li>
            <li>Sharing or selling illegal content</li>
            <li>Encouraging illegal activities</li>
            <li>Copyright infringement or intellectual property theft</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>üö´ Platform Abuse</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Creating multiple accounts to evade bans</li>
            <li>Impersonating others or misrepresenting identity</li>
            <li>Attempting to manipulate the algorithm unfairly</li>
            <li>Hacking or unauthorized access attempts</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Enforcement</h2>
        <p>When content or behavior violates these guidelines, we may take action including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Content Removal:</strong> We'll remove violating posts, comments, or media</li>
            <li><strong>Warning:</strong> First-time minor violations may result in a warning</li>
            <li><strong>Temporary Suspension:</strong> Repeated or serious violations lead to temporary account suspension</li>
            <li><strong>Permanent Ban:</strong> Severe or persistent violations result in permanent account termination</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Reporting Violations</h2>
        <p>If you see content or behavior that violates these guidelines:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Use the "Report" button on any post or profile</li>
            <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:moderation@dreamx.com">moderation@dreamx.com</a></li>
            <li>For urgent safety concerns, contact <a href="mailto:safety@dreamx.com">safety@dreamx.com</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Appeals</h2>
        <p>If you believe we made a mistake in enforcing these guidelines:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>For content removals: <a href="/content-appeal">Submit a Content Appeal</a></li>
            <li>For account actions: <a href="/account-appeal">Submit an Account Appeal</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>We review all appeals within 48 hours.</p>

        <h2>Context Matters</h2>
        <p>We understand that context is important. Educational content, artistic expression, and social commentary may include sensitive topics. We'll consider context when evaluating potential violations.</p>

        <h2>Updates to Guidelines</h2>
        <p>These guidelines may be updated as our community grows and evolves. We'll notify users of significant changes and always maintain our commitment to creating a positive, growth-focused environment.</p>

        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these guidelines, contact us at <a href="mailto:community@dreamx.com">community@dreamx.com</a> or visit our <a href="/help-center">Help Center</a>.</p>
